{"abstract": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/talk/6770", "blasters": ["perl"], "description": "<a href=\"https://www.debian.org/\">Debian</a> is one of the largest and oldest Free Operating Systems.\n<a href=\"https://pkg-perl.alioth.debian.org/\">The Debian Perl Group</a> makes CPAN distributions available to users of Debian and its derivates as Debian packages.\nThis talk gives an overview of the group's work, and presents some ideas to the Perl community how CPAN authors can make our work even easier.\n\n<ul>\n   <li>Changes file</li>\n   <li>Include resources in the META files</li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://github.com/Perl-Toolchain-Gang/toolchain-site/blob/master/lancaster-consensus.md\">Lancester consensus</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"http://qa-hackathon.org/\">QA Hackathon</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/Test::Spelling\">Test::Spelling</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://metacpan.org/pod/Dist::Zilla\">Dist::Zilla</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n", "event": {"name": "YAPC - European Perl Conference 2016", "nickname": "yapc-eu-2016", "twitter": "yapceu", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/"}, "favorite": "0", "featured": "2016-12-29", "file_date": "2016-12-03", "filename": "alex-muntada-from-debian-with-yapceurope-2016", "length": "56:51", "likes": "1", "recorded": "2016-08-24", "short_description": "Debian is one of the largest and oldest Free Operating Systems. The Debian Perl Group makes CPAN distributions available to user", "speaker_twitters": " @alexmuntada", "speakers": {"alex-muntada": {"episodes": [], "hosting": [], "info": {"city": "Barcelona", "country": "Spain", "github": "alexm", "home": "http://log.alexm.org/", "name": "Alex Muntada", "twitter": "alexmuntada"}, "videos": [{"event": {"name": "YAPC - European Perl Conference 2016", "nickname": "yapc-eu-2016", "twitter": "yapceu", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/"}, "filename": "alex-muntada-from-debian-with-yapceurope-2016", "recorded": "2016-08-24", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/BrdwNvly